<h1>Scoring</h1>

<h3>How is my pudge score determined?</h3>

<p>
  Currently, there is your rank is determined by your hook accuracy against enemy heroes. 
</p>

<p>
  In the future, your pudge score will be determined by a combination of stats and events gathered from the replay. This metric will be used as the main ranking mechanism.
</p>
